        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", and which would explain Both the Hebrew and the Septuagint words. An Indian site for Ophir would also well suit the mention of the ivory and the particular wood which the ships brought. On the other hand, the first occasion of this name Ophir finds it placed among the tribes of ",
        "children": []
